title: Independence Day 2022 Special - The Dan Bongino Show
description:
First, Dan rants about the SCOTUS 2A decision from last week, "the left doesn't understand us but we understand them". Then Dan breaking down the left, and their choice of subjectivity vs. objectivity. Finally, Dan breaks down the left's extinction burst, and discusses Stacey Abrams abortion interview
